      <Placemark>
        <name>AI Council Assessment</name>
        <styleUrl>#intel</styleUrl>
        <description>The U.S. military continues to expand its defense budget, focusing on new technologies such as Tomahawks and SM-6s. The Marines are conducting live-fire exercises with drones, while the Navy is deploying ships in the Philippines due to ongoing operations. The Green Berets successfully avoid detection by drones during a training scenario. Maintenance competitions among aviation soldiers highlight their skills, and Command Sgt. Maj. Jeremy Bunkley discusses leadership within the U.S. Army Garrison.</description>
        <Point>
